  "remarks": "Nizhny Novgorod Sokol Aircraft Plant is a Russian aviation company. It is a contractor of the Ministry of Defence of the Russian Federation. It maintains and modernises the MiG-31 interceptor aircraft of the Armed Forces of the Russian Federation under the State defence order. Some of the modernised MiG-31 are equipped with the Kinzhal hypersonic air-launched ballistic missiles.",
